{
  "id": "6a1a64a89226792cf7de45bb",
  "title": "泥沼の闘争の構造",
  "created": 1780114601,
  "updated": 1780118644,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a89226792cf7de45bb",
      "text": "泥沼の闘争の構造",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b65",
      "text": "from [2026/05/30]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114605
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b67",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b68",
      "text": " 派閥の二項対立に見えるものはシンプルな派閥の二項対立じゃなくてもっと込み入っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b69",
      "text": " \tと言うか、主戦場がシンプルな派閥の二項対立部分じゃない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6a",
      "text": " \t例えば：きのこ派とたけのこ派で争っているように見えるとき",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a659f0000000000bb1b7d",
      "text": "  \t[https://gyazo.com/80953c570cc7f8d166c2f2ac363c1c83]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114848,
      "updated": 1780114885
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6b",
      "text": " \t\tきのこ派とたけのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6c",
      "text": " \t\tきのこ派と反きのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6d",
      "text": " \t\tたけのこ派と反たけのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6e",
      "text": " \t\t反きのこ派と反反きのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b6f",
      "text": " \t\t反たけのこ派と反反たけのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b70",
      "text": " \t\t反反きのこ派とたけのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b71",
      "text": " \t\t反反たけのこ派ときのこ派が争っている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a691b0000000000bb1b80",
      "text": " \t\t[https://gyazo.com/489596a20e372f6a2de3f2c843ceede2]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780115740,
      "updated": 1780115742
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6ba50000000000bb1b8a",
      "text": " \t\t\t反反きのこ派にハートが付いているのは反きのこ派が付けた禁止マークに対抗してきのこ派アピールを強めたがっている様子を表現",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116390,
      "updated": 1780116483
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6c020000000000bb1b8b",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t対抗意識みたいな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116483,
      "updated": 1780116488
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6c130000000000bb1b8c",
      "text": " \t\t\t\tきのこ派と反反きのこ派はこの辺に違いがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116499,
      "updated": 1780116520
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6c530000000000bb1b8d",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t反反きのこ派はきのこ派から見ると味方につけるには鬱陶しい感じ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116564,
      "updated": 1780116613
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6c9d0000000000bb1b8e",
      "text": " \t\t\t\t\t敵の敵は味方理論は同盟を組むための理屈であって、本当に味方とは限らない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116638,
      "updated": 1780116673
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b72",
      "text": " \tみたいな感じの構図ができていたとして、外部から見ると",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b73",
      "text": " \t\t外部から見たきのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b74",
      "text": " \t\t\tきのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b75",
      "text": " \t\t\t反たけのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b76",
      "text": " \t\t\t反反きのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b77",
      "text": " \t\t外部から見たたけのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b78",
      "text": " \t\t\tたけのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b79",
      "text": " \t\t\t反きのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b7a",
      "text": " \t\t\t反反たけのこ派",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a65760000000000a1493a",
      "text": " \t\tすぐ内ゲバする[caki.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1780114807,
      "updated": 1780118644
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a0d0000000000bb1b83",
      "text": " \t\t[https://gyazo.com/f077e21f0d2a241c640ef8aa4eb62874]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780115982,
      "updated": 1780115984
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a64a80000000000bb1b7b",
      "text": " \tみたいになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780114601,
      "updated": 1780114601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a800000000000bb1b86",
      "text": " 状況が複雑になるにしてもこんな感じにはならない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116097,
      "updated": 1780116126
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a8f0000000000bb1b88",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/87e79c1a8bd51f4674773df59d4ba5c5]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780116112,
      "updated": 1780116114
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6f9800000000003c8d36",
      "text": "  新勢力[きたきたのこのこの山里]も登場した[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780117394,
      "updated": 1780117419
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1a6a910000000000bb1b89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
